kabegame-plasma-wallpaper (0.1.2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix config panel crash on second open: ThumbnailProvider was a static
    singleton given to QQmlEngine via addImageProvider(), so the engine took
    ownership and deleted it when the first config closed, leaving a dangling
    pointer. Second open then triggered use-after-free when loading gallery
    thumbnails. Fix: move thumbnail path storage to ThumbnailPathStore, create
    a new ThumbnailProvider per engine in initializeEngine() so each engine
    owns its provider and no use-after-free occurs.

 -- Cmtheit <cmtheit@outlook.com>  Fri, 20 Mar 2025 12:00:00 +0800

